videos.description: Chet Holmgren finds a wide-open Julian Strawther for the 3-pointer to extend the Bulldogs' lead.
videos.headline: Julian Strawther finds nothing but net as he drains the 3 for Gonzaga

videos.description: Chet Holmgren says not in my house as he swats away the rock for the massive block.
videos.headline: Chet Holmgren with the massive rejection for Gonzaga

videos.description: Chet Holmgren elevates and throws down the lob from Nolan Hickman to extend the Bulldogs' lead.
videos.headline: Chet Holmgren elevates for throw down on alley-oop

videos.description: Andrew Nembhard crosses his defender and finishes with the smooth layup for the Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Andrew Nembhard makes a nice move for the layup) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Andrew Nembhard is smooth as silk as he drains the layup for Gonzaga

videos.description: Chet Holmgren is unstoppable as he elevates and denies BYU at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Chet Holmgren with the massive block at the rim) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chet Holmgren elevates for the monstrous block for Gonzaga

videos.description: Chet Holmgren with the absolute dime to Drew Timme for the bucket, extending the Bulldogs' lead early in the second half.
videos.headline: Chet Holmgren finds Drew Timme for the Gonzaga bucket

videos.description: Chet Holmgren drives on the baseline and muscles through his defender for the and-1.
videos.headline: Chet Holmgren won't be denied as he drains the and-1 for Gonzaga

videos.description: Julian Strawther loses his footing and somehow knocks down the and-1 for the Bulldogs late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Julian Strawther gets the and-1 to fall) 2022/02/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Julian Strawther somehow drains the and-1 for Gonzaga
